 ('3760','NI-OH','ps3','8','20','http://www.koei.com','','Announcing the tale of a blonde-haired, blue-eyed warrior in civil war Japan - the ultimate in Action Entertainment! In the civil war era of feudal Japan A blonde-haired, blue-eyed warrior of mixed parentage. Must carve his own fate By throwing himself into the tides of war... ','RP','1','6','2005-05-16','2007-04-30'),
