 ('5712','Kane & Lynch: Dead Men','PC','250','6',null,'','Kane &amp; Lynch: Dead Men is a violent and chaotic journey of two men - a flawed mercenary and a medicated psychopath – and their brutal attitude towards right and wrong. This volatile partnership combined with innovative technologies allow for an unparalleled gaming experience. ','RP','1','3','2007-01-12','2007-07-11'),
 ('5713','Kane & Lynch: Dead Men','360','250','6',null,'shots/360/5713_1184196385.jpg','Kane &amp; Lynch: Dead Men is a violent and chaotic journey of two men - a flawed mercenary and a medicated psychopath – and their brutal attitude towards right and wrong. This volatile partnership combined with innovative technologies allow for an unparalleled gaming experience. ','RP','1','3','2007-01-12','2007-07-11'),
