 ('6548','Heroes','ps3','132','13',null,'','\"Heroes” is an epic drama that chronicles the lives of ordinary people across the world who discover they possess extraordinary abilities, such as telepathy, time travel and flight. They will soon come to realize that the fate of the world depends on them, and be forced to team up against someone seeking to eliminate them.','RP','1','3','2007-07-27','2007-07-27'),
 ('6549','Heroes','PC','132','13',null,'','\"Heroes” is an epic drama that chronicles the lives of ordinary people across the world who discover they possess extraordinary abilities, such as telepathy, time travel and flight. They will soon come to realize that the fate of the world depends on them, and be forced to team up against someone seeking to eliminate them.','RP','1','3','2007-07-27','2007-07-27'),
